snippet.title: FNAF AR Dark Circus: Encore!
snippet.description:
May we present...
The Dark Circus: Encore!--in full mixed reality as you've never seen it before. Come see Great Escape Golden Freddy & stunning spectacles galore! The only question is...can you leave, once you walk through the door?

Explore & find your way through a brand-new Dark Circus MR environment with animatronics both familiar and new! Plenty of gameplay, puzzles, and surprises await!
